en_813876_0	COLOMBO (News1st) – Dinesh Gunawardene has been appointed as the Minister of Megapolis and Western Development.
en_813876_1	Vasudeva Nanayakkara was sworn in as the Minister of National Integration, Reconciliation, and Official Languages.
en_813876_2	Keheliya Rambukwella was appointed as the State Minister of Mass Media and Digital Infrastructure while UNP MP R.D. Ashoka Priyantha was sworn in as Deputy Minister of Cultural and Internal Affairs, and Regional Development (Wayamba).
en_813876_3	This was confirmed through Media Spokesperson for the government Keheliya Rambukwella.
